---
title: Sesame-Crusted Salmon with Roasted Potatoes, Broccoli and Lemon Aioli
description: Sesame-kissed salmon steals the spotlight in tonight's fish special! Roasted potatoes dolloped with lemon aioli are the perfect co-stars.
